<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/styles.css" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;700&family=Lato:wght@300;400;700&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles/normalize.css" />

    <title>FireNet</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <section>
      <div class="background">
        <h2>Wild File Predictor</h2>
        <h1>
          You are currently in a <a class="h1--result"><%= output; %></a> fire
          severity area.
        </h1>
        <h4>As based on 55,000 historical wildfires.</h4>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section4">
      <h2>Results</h2>
      <p class="conditions">
        If you are in a <a class="h1--result">low </a> fire severity area...
      </p>
      <ul class="list--style">
        <li>wildfires occur rarely here, and are relatively small.</li>
        <li>Be mindful if campfires, bonfires, and other outdoor burns.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="conditions">
        If you are in a <a class="h1--result">medium </a> fire severity area...
      </p>
      <ul class="list--style">
        <li>wildfires may get moderately large here (up to 1,000 acres).</li>
        <li>
          Reconsider outdoor burns and pay attention for dry weather conditions.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="conditions">
        If you are in a <a class="h1--result">high </a> fire severity area...
      </p>
      <ul class="list--style">
        <li>
          Wildfires occur relatively frequently here, and are often over 1,000
          acres
        </li>
        <li>Restrict any outdoor burns and be vigiant for rising smoke.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </body>
</html>
